{
  "stem": "979.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So there were three of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was my sister, my-- and my sister, her husband, and me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The six of us-- they took us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the train that they put us in, they put us with the crippled people, because my-- my cousin had no legs.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And all the crippled were there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so we were in the same train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, going to Germany.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the train was so terrible, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like they didn't have seats, that whatever-- they described the trains.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That it was like a cattle train-- train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my-- my brother-in-law, he was-- spoke German so well.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he took over in the train to talk and everything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was helping people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it took us eight days.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we had all our stuff.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We know, we were well dressed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We brought our-- all our-- we had money.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We had jewelry, because thinking that we need everything, at least the things we could bring.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the eighth day, when we got there, it was the most horrible thing I ever saw.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was 10:00, 11:00 at night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I don't remember the time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But it was very dark.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And suddenly, as we got off, there was whistles-- people, you know-- like Nazis running and whistling, and with the dogs, and things saying [NON-ENGLISH]!",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we saw.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What is this?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were looking.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We say, where are we?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the meantime, we passed through Budapest and that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We saw the river, you know, the Nile.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We saw nice things as we were passing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we were locked in the train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't think they give us food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we had our own things that we brought things.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
